[Information on the monthly assessment of polio eradication efforts
current as of 29 Jan 2009 can be found at
<http://www.polioeradication.org/content/general/current_monthly_sitrep.asp>.

Information on WPV confirmations by year since 2000 is available at
<http://www.polioeradication.org/content/general/casecount.pdf>.

Importations into previously polio free countries from Nigeria and
now Sudan continue to occur in 2008 and 2009. The current political
strife in the Sudan does not bode well for control of WPV
circulation. - Mod.MPP]
